title: Grammy's Favorite Knits for Baby
description:
When you want to knit something special for a sweet little someone, Grammy's got the pattern! Featuring attractive, uncomplicated projects that won't go out of fashion with the latest trend, this collection is brimming with baby-gift classics.

* Choose from cute and cuddly baby blankets, layette pieces, hats, booties, mitts, and even sweaters

* Find more than 20 quick-to-knit projects in sizes from infant to 24 months

* Create the perfect gift every time
